{"tid":1642014,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有無人開始有寧願老解入城攬炒既打算？","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T00:56:24.000Z","uid":36134,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b44d70330182598c8b3c95d2b3c73e177aceb6c9","tid":1642014,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"每日起碼幾單黑警迫害 污辱香港人既新聞<br />\n<br />\n寧願老解入城大家攬炒<br />\n都好過而家班黑警無法無天<br />\n不斷挑戰香港人底線<br />\n不斷迫害香港人<br />\n屌你老母 越黎越有攬炒既打算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真，有時你想停<br />\n對面只會繼續迫害 追殺 唔好會停架<br />\n班狗而家當正我地賤民咁對待<br />\n希望以後大家唔好再阻止勇武任何行動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要有攬炒既覺悟</span></span>"},{"pid":"6bc20f09d5e0f2d06a2dc13714a2c3265c2a1a31","tid":1642014,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82857c4b6d98c7c411b84a91cd63108c82e3a3d3","tid":1642014,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00860a1bfd893e79dba67dec32c2a20aee7df1a","tid":1642014,"uid":41352,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"香港人一早準備左，係佢地死都唔會做咁解"},{"pid":"e2d318ac00819c54706b2696f3cea9218efb5b91","tid":1642014,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1a18cc7b8f9917741372bf5b7a2a154565a0a95","tid":1642014,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7840c27a98f4c66e7069b5410029c3bbdaddade","tid":1642014,"uid":312526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"我聽d街坊講多左人接受攬炒"},{"pid":"1024466de45d246b77026140092d31501e3aedaf","tid":1642014,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-